### Competitors and Adjacents[^15]


#### Competitors {#competitors}



*   [https://www.captec.io/](https://www.captec.io/) - Capital is set up at the intersection of tech and finance to solve capital access problems in an automated and tech-enabled way.
*   [http://www.pointfin.com/](http://www.pointfin.com/) - Point Financial, Inc. has a mission to provide flexible, entrepreneurial financing for emerging market companies to reach their financial goals, achieve positive liquidity with less equity funding
*   [https://www.htgc.com/](https://www.htgc.com/) - Hercules was founded with a vision to serve the needs of both entrepreneurs and investors, in providing an alternative investment vehicle 

Adjacents



*   Consumer lending [https://borrowell.com/](https://borrowell.com/) - consumer access toa free credit score with personalized tips, tools and offers to fit the user’s financial goals.
*   Financial Services [https://www.waveapps.com/](https://www.waveapps.com/) - An award-winning financial services software company serving small business owners and freelancers
*   Payments financing [https://www.financeit.io/](https://www.financeit.io/) - flexible, mobile-friendly, sales boosting financing at checkout for ecommerce entrepreneurs and their web and mobile sites
*   Capital lending operations [https://www.kooltra.com/](https://www.kooltra.com/) - cloud-based solutions to digitize and automate post-trade operations, risk and compliance


